; figure8.gcode — Figure-8 in XZ plane at Y=80
; Two tangent circles, radius 25mm each
; Centered at X=190, Z=0
G90
G1 X190 Y80 Z0 F20

; Right loop
G1 X210 Y80 Z6 F20
G1 X215 Y80 Z25 F20
G1 X210 Y80 Z44 F20
G1 X190 Y80 Z50 F20
G1 X170 Y80 Z44 F20
G1 X165 Y80 Z25 F20
G1 X170 Y80 Z6 F20

; Cross back
G1 X190 Y80 Z0 F20

; Left loop
G1 X210 Y80 Z-6 F20
G1 X215 Y80 Z-25 F20
G1 X210 Y80 Z-44 F20
G1 X190 Y80 Z-50 F20
G1 X170 Y80 Z-44 F20
G1 X165 Y80 Z-25 F20
G1 X170 Y80 Z-6 F20

; Return
G1 X190 Y80 Z0 F20
